{"tid":1618163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒唔到]唔好再講蒙面法, 要講<<緊急法>>","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:56:04.000Z","uid":218313,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b0127d4dd01742e2522be16a722dd2b5d02b4327","tid":1618163,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔成個方向<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">錯。撚。晒</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家應該要講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&lt;&lt;緊急法&gt;&gt;</strong></span></span><br />\n唔係講咩反蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家全香港只係講緊蒙面<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林病用 &lt;&lt;緊急法&gt;&gt; 繞過立法局, 夾硬將條法例上巿, 係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">無。人。講</span></span>!</span><br />\n完全俾政府SPIN 走晒重點<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: maroon;\">無人留意點攬炒???</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊急法<span style=\"color: orange;\">威力無邊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以限制人出入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n充公財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲乜法都任佢立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我敢講有一次就有第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重申: </span><ins>唔好再講蒙面法, 呢條法例對我地係無用<br />\n非法集會夠犯法啦, 要出都會照出</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><ins>要講就要講&lt;緊急法&gt;, 解釋一下呢條法例威力點勁<br />\n等D 港豬/商人驚先有用!!</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極權緊急法<br />\n銀紙變垃圾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推!"},{"pid":"e7e95229b7f5f75befcfe311f60d87443cc1728d","tid":1618163,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"推1<br />\n極權緊急法<br />\n銀紙變垃圾"},{"pid":"d7f3e04891ed81a598b533c2b43828dde68e45d8","tid":1618163,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69adbeb30e3e17c47d563ba00207a366670aa27","tid":1618163,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"有無文宣圖?"},{"pid":"d9e6528ce5b958c95007a0bf11ef8a3c4565f65f","tid":1618163,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法治變垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea49d3b5bb0901c1cae666948bb1b86f69e21d88","tid":1618163,"uid":203179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd2ef868b4b21cf7fd4081ec183c0b1a23c4d094","tid":1618163,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"陣間落樓就嗌呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bd5cfcc022cd103140affcee964985ecf3ff76","tid":1618163,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"149b3c9df28a27509d0dfb3272ed4860902ce75e","tid":1618163,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"三權合一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a38a7908